            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (5)

- Removes the first-use update dialog icon scan that could delay the update-check window by several seconds.
- Keeps the immediate update-check feedback path from build 4, with timing diagnostics around the dialog and Sparkle handoff.
]]></description>
